    <div class="main review-item" id="6827801">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6827801/" class="title-link">“何等幸运，邂逅此君”</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6827801"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/Broken-jade/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1045817-3.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Broken-jade/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">斗室的碎玉</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-08-17"
      class="main-meta">2014-08-17 21:12:07</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6827801_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  对于这两册书，我有太多感触，反而不知如何着手。  随着人的年岁渐长，一个人读书的感受也会逐渐变化。三十岁之后读书，恐怕只有很少人是为了学业、文凭，因此读书的动机因人而异，异常复杂。但共同点总是有的：好奇心。无论是对未知世界的无尽探求，还是对于热点事件、知名人...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/6827801/#comments">(3回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">81有用 / 8没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_6827801_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_6827801_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="7437331">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7437331/" class="title-link">《文明之光》到底讲什么？</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7437331"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/40484032/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u40484032-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/40484032/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">Ryan</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2015-04-07"
      class="main-meta">2015-04-07 22:41:37</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7437331_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  书是好书，不用说。但粗略看了下评论，似乎很少人（我只看到一位）看明白这套书到底在讲什么。很多人都只是把这套书当成历史书来看，更有民族主义者认为作者想表达“崖山之后再无中国”，简直可笑至极。  吴军作为一个科学家，跨界写历史，而书名是“文明之光”，而非“文明史...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/7437331/#comments">(10回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">65有用 / 4没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_7437331_full" class="hidden">
